{"name":"The Green Path","type":"Power","img":"systems/worldofdarkness/assets/img/items/mainpower_vampire.svg","system":{"iscreated":true,"version":"2.2.0","parentid":"","worldanvil":"","reference":"V20 215","description":"<p>The Green Path deals with the manipulation of plant matter of all sorts. Anything more complex than an algae bloom can theoretically be controlled through the appropriate application of this path. Ferns, roses, dandelions, and even ancient redwoods are all valid targets for this path&rsquo;s powers, and living and dead plant matter are equally affected. While not as immediately impressive as some other more widely practiced paths, the Green Path (sometimes disparagingly referred to as &ldquo;Botanical Mastery&rdquo;) is as subtle and powerful as the natural world which it affects.</p>","details":"","type":"wod.types.disciplinepath","level":"0","value":0,"max":5,"dice1":"","dice2":"","bonus":0,"difficulty":0,"isrollable":false,"isactive":false,"spendwillpower":false,"spendrage":false,"spendgnosis":false,"spendblood":false,"spendglamour":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_khzqb46fpao","path":"Disciplines#/CF_SEP/Thaumaturgy#/CF_SEP/Thaumaturgy Paths#/CF_SEP/The Green Path","color":"#000000"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"worldofdarkness","systemVersion":"2.2.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1671007123413,"modifiedTime":1674439741288,"lastModifiedBy":"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc"},"_id":"1xzc6rCz4TTqyeyj","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc":3}}
{"name":"●●●●● Telecommute","type":"Power","img":"systems/worldofdarkness/assets/img/items/power_vampire.svg","system":{"iscreated":true,"version":"2.2.0","parentid":"","worldanvil":"","reference":"V20 226","description":"<p>A progressive derivation of Remote Access, Telecommute allows a thaumaturge to project her consciousness into the Internet, sending her mind through network connections as fast as they can transfer her. While immersed in the network, she can use any other Technomancy power on the devices with which she makes contact.</p>","details":"<p>The character touches any form of communications device: a cellphone, 3G-equipped netbook, Wi-Fi tablet, or anything else that is connected directly or indirectly to the Internet. The player rolls normally and spends a Willpower point. Telecommute lasts for five minutes per success rolled, and may be extended by 10 minutes with the expenditure of another Willpower point. The number of successes indicates the maximum range that the character can project her consciousness away from her body:<br><br></p>\n<table border=\"1\"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Successes</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Result</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1 Success</td>\n<td>25 miles/40 kilometers</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2 Successes</td>\n<td>250 miles/400 kilometers</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3 Successes</td>\n<td>1000 miles/1500 kilometers</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4 Successes</td>\n<td>5000 miles/8000 kilometers</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5 Successes</td>\n<td>Anywhere in the world</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><br>While in the network, the character can apply any other Path of Technomancy power to any device or data with which she comes in contact. A loss of connection, either through the destruction of a part of the network or simply a loss of cell signal, hurls her consciousness back to her body and inflicts eight dice of bashing damage.<br><br>A character traveling through the Internet by means of this power can use her Path of Technomancy powers at a normal difficulty. Using any other abilities or powers while engaged thus is done at a +2 difficulty.</p>","type":"wod.types.disciplinepathpower","level":"5","value":0,"max":5,"dice1":"willpower","dice2":"","bonus":0,"difficulty":"8","isrollable":true,"isactive":false,"spendwillpower":false,"spendrage":false,"spendgnosis":false,"spendblood":false,"spendglamour":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_w0iir3wpc8q","path":"Disciplines#/CF_SEP/Thaumaturgy#/CF_SEP/Thaumaturgy Paths#/CF_SEP/The Path of Technomancy","color":"#000000"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"worldofdarkness","systemVersion":"2.2.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670931559691,"modifiedTime":1674439746965,"lastModifiedBy":"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc"},"_id":"20G6Olc0WGsmZpYU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc":3}}
