{"name":"Hands of Destruction","type":"Power","img":"systems/worldofdarkness/assets/img/items/mainpower_vampire.svg","system":{"iscreated":true,"version":"2.2.0","parentid":"","worldanvil":"","reference":"V20 217","description":"<p>This Path is practiced most commonly by the various thaumaturges of the Sabbat. Though it is not widely seen outside that Sect, a few Camarilla Tremere have managed to learn the secrets of this path over the centuries. The Hands of Destruction has an infamous history, and some Tremere refuse to practice it due to rumors that it is demonic in origin.</p>","details":"","type":"wod.types.disciplinepath","level":"0","value":0,"max":5,"dice1":"","dice2":"","bonus":0,"difficulty":0,"isrollable":false,"isactive":false,"spendwillpower":false,"spendrage":false,"spendgnosis":false,"spendblood":false,"spendglamour":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_qrx4b8dkuga","path":"Disciplines#/CF_SEP/Thaumaturgy#/CF_SEP/Thaumaturgy Paths#/CF_SEP/Hands of Destruction","color":"#000000"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"worldofdarkness","systemVersion":"2.2.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1671008167998,"modifiedTime":1674439738018,"lastModifiedBy":"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc"},"_id":"AiK6oByi33Heoj41","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc":3}}
{"name":"Recruitment Target (1pt. Flaw)","type":"Feature","img":"systems/worldofdarkness/assets/img/items/feature.svg","system":{"iscreated":true,"version":"2.2.5","parentid":"","worldanvil":"","reference":"V20 490","description":"<p>Someone in one of your Sect&rsquo;s enemy organizations wants you, and they want you bad. Every effort is being made to recruit you, willing or no, and the press gangs usually show up at the worst possible time.</p>","details":"<p>Social</p>","type":"wod.types.flaw","level":"1","value":0,"max":5,"isrollable":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PObtkAVWkJjHBqr7"},"cf":{"id":"temp_jwd9ok2vgth","path":"Merits & Flaws#/CF_SEP/Flaws#/CF_SEP/1 pt. Flaws","color":"#000000"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"worldofdarkness","systemVersion":"2.2.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672474316434,"modifiedTime":1674221102528,"lastModifiedBy":"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc"},"_id":"AlJW95PGvscHSg6z","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc":3}}
