{"name":"Cursed (1-5pt. Flaw)","type":"Feature","img":"systems/worldofdarkness/assets/img/items/feature.svg","system":{"iscreated":true,"version":"2.2.5","parentid":"","worldanvil":"","reference":"V20 494","description":"<p>You are the recipient of a supernatural curse. The strength and pervasiveness of the curse depend upon how many points you wish to incur. Examples follow:<br><br>&bull; If you pass on a secret you were entrusted with, your betrayal will come back to harm you in some way. (1 pt.)<br><br>&bull; You stutter uncontrollably when you try to describe what you have seen or heard. (2 pts.)<br><br>&bull; Tools break or malfunction when you try to use them. (3 pts.)<br><br>&bull; You are doomed to make enemies of those whom you most love or admire. (4 pts.)<br><br>&bull; Every one of your accomplishments or triumphs will eventually become soiled or fail in some way. (5 pts.)</p>","details":"<p>Supernatural</p>","type":"wod.types.flaw","level":"","value":0,"max":5,"isrollable":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PObtkAVWkJjHBqr7"},"cf":{"id":"temp_d9j4thjusi","path":"Merits & Flaws#/CF_SEP/Flaws#/CF_SEP/Multi-pt. Flaws","color":"#000000"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"worldofdarkness","systemVersion":"2.2.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1672474316434,"modifiedTime":1674221113809,"lastModifiedBy":"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc"},"_id":"oQFesSnrCWpEO7p3","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc":3}}
{"name":"● Cloak of Shadows","type":"Power","img":"systems/worldofdarkness/assets/img/items/power_vampire.svg","system":{"iscreated":true,"version":"2.2.0","parentid":"","worldanvil":"","reference":"V20 184","description":"<p>At this level, the vampire must rely on nearby shadows and cover to assist in hiding his presence. He steps into an out-of-the-way, shadowed place and eases himself from normal sight. The vampire remains unnoticed as long as he stays silent, still, under some degree of cover (such as a curtain, bush, door frame, lamppost, or alley), and out of direct lighting. The immortal&rsquo;s concealment vanishes if he moves, attacks, or falls under direct light. Furthermore, the vampire&rsquo;s deception cannot stand up to concentrated observation without fading.</p>","details":"<p>No roll is required as long as the character fulfills the criteria described above. So long as he remains quiet and motionless, virtually no one but another Kindred with a high enough Auspex rating will see him.</p>","type":"wod.types.disciplinepower","level":"1","value":0,"max":5,"dice1":"","dice2":"","bonus":0,"difficulty":"","isrollable":false,"isactive":false,"spendwillpower":false,"spendrage":false,"spendgnosis":false,"spendblood":false,"spendglamour":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_va4nd0abdk","path":"Disciplines#/CF_SEP/Obfuscate","color":"#000000"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"worldofdarkness","systemVersion":"2.2.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1670294183933,"modifiedTime":1674221177295,"lastModifiedBy":"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc"},"_id":"oR91QlDptEGCRMbg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"CZyj5tVpsqRvDFFc":3}}
